metadata.name: Her Birth
metadata.description:
She was born that day. Silently, imperceptible and for no apparent reason. I do not remember exactly what I was thinking before it happened, but there must have been a trigger. Some kind of idea, some kind of thought loop that started the process. But, she might as well have been there all along. In fact, it is very likely.

Nib pen & ink on paper 
15040x7472px
